data.description: Lake access to all Sports Baw Beese Lake. This 3 bedroom is a very solid home that sits on 2 lots with road access on 2 roads. The kitchen is quite large which allows for eating and entertaining. Also included is a rear enclosed porch that overlooks the spacious rear yard and a wood insert fireplace that the seller uses to this day. With a few cosmetic touches, this home can definitely be transformed into a very comfortable home.
